---
title: Mediterranean-Style Bocconcini Orzo with Garlic Bread
description: Tangy mixed olives and creamy bocconcini pearls come together to bring bold flavour to this savoury Mediterranean-style orzo. A side of garlic bread to scoop up every bite makes the meal complete!
